				17 = alignCanceled
				18 = warning: see automaticAlignmentLastRunErrorIndex to figure out entry of automaticAlignmentOptionsTable to see the last warning.
				19 = error: see automaticAlignmentLastRunErrorIndex to figure out entry of automaticAlignmentOptionsTable to see the first error.
				20 = unknown module
				21 = error: slope below low limit / slope too low
				22 = error: slope above high limit / slope too high
				23 = warning: slope near low limit / slope too low
				24 = warning: slope near high limit / slope too high
				25 = error: gain below low limit
				26 = error: gain above high limit
				27 = warning: gain near low limit
				28 = warning: gain near high limit
				
				Status is set to 1, when device boots up."
