			ACCESS read-only
			STATUS mandatory
			DESCRIPTION
				"Same status codes than pilotBasedAlignmentStatus.
				1 = never run
				2 = running
				3 = success
				4 = no tuner module
				5 = targets out of range
				6 = interstage slope target ouf of range
				7 = pilots not found
				8 = input slope out of range
				9 = gain target out of range
				10 = a cable simulator may be needed into the universal plug-in slot
				11 = gain or slope is saturated
				12 = unknown forward path plug-in module
				13 = alignGain2TargetOutOfRange / auxGainOutOfRange
				14 = alignInterStage2SlopeOutOfRange
				15 = alignOpticalInputPowerOutOfRange
				16 = alignWaitingForRun
